data.details: GSSJC is seeking volunteers to work with girls on the challenge course (AKA ropes course)! This one-day training will familiarize you with the process that facilitators use to guide groups of girls through the challenge course by using outdoor educational processing, team building, group cooperation activities, and offer you the opportunity to experience some of the low elements yourself. No climbing required!
